_source.title: PPM API - Logged HL7v2 message
_source.description: Shows segments of the HL7v2 message that were logged.

_source.title: PPM API - Full Message Path
_source.description: Shows all logging to trace a message through the critical path in PPM API

_source.title: PPM API - Send Receive
_source.description: Logs when the message to PharmaNet was sent and a response received.

_source.title: PPM API - Transaction UUID
_source.description: Shows logging that has the Transaction UUID field which can be used to track a single transaction's progress by adding a filter for the UUID value.

_source.title: PPM API - Trace ID
_source.description: Shows logging which contains a trace ID that is added as an HTTP Header in the API Gateway. This can be used to track messages between the API Gateway and PPM API.
